    "body" : "<p><strong>1320917972</strong> is Unix timestamp using number of seconds since 00:00:00 UTC on January 1, 1970. You can use <code>TimeUnit</code> class for unit conversion - from <code>System.currentTimeMillis()</code> to seconds.</p>\n\n<pre><code>String timeStamp = String.valueOf(TimeUnit.MILLISECONDS.toSeconds(System.currentTimeMillis()));\n</code></pre>\n"
